{"tid":120629,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死9隻]湖南煤礦爆炸13人被困　9死4獲救","createTime":"2017-02-14T14:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T14:30:39.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6fa5e191c24cfed3f348a7fa56ce3536e133909d","tid":120629,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T14:30:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170214/bkncn-20170214091240195-0214_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170214%2Fbkncn-20170214091240195-0214_05011_001.html&d=Q0Uk0WlElUZ8hxv%2Fjb96J5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=cefc1877\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170214/bkncn-20170214091240195-0214_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170214/photo/bkncn-20170214091240195-0214_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170214%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170214091240195-0214_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=0b73d579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖南省婁底市漣源市斗笠山鎮祖保煤礦，今日凌晨1時37分左右發生爆炸事故。據報事發時共有29名礦工在井下工作，其中16人安全升井。救援人員接報到場搜救其餘13人，救出4名被困者，9人在事故中死亡。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該礦為鄉鎮煤礦，核定生產能力每年9萬噸，屬高瓦斯礦井。事故後國家安全監管總局要求湖南省安監局、湖南煤監局調集周邊救援力量及專家，協助地方政府搜救，嚴防發生次生事故，又要求核清事故有關情況，查明事故原因，依法依規嚴肅追責。<br />\n<br />\n情人節快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}